                        %small.text-light.target
                  .card-body
                    .donut_chart
                    .animated-background
            .row.mt-3
              .col-12.sankey_chart_div
                .card.border-primary
                  .card-header.bg-primary
                    %h5.card-title.text-white
                      %i.fa.fa-random.fa-fw
                      Sankey Chart
                    %p
                      %small.text-light
                        Shows receive traffic flows from the left side (AS) to the right (Interfaces). Thickness represents volume of traffic. Put your mouse over a node to show actual values.
                  .card-body
